idinfo.accconst: Data will be made available free of charge for all internal uses and for those companies with contracts is good standing with the City of Norfolk. All others are required to purchase the data from the City of Norfolk, Department of Public Works, Surveys Division.
idinfo.useconst: Any and all data sets are for graphical representation only and should not be used for legal purposes. Any determination of topography or contours, or any depiction of physical improvements, property lines or boundaries is for general information only and shall not be used for the design, modification, or construction of improvements to real property or for flood plain determination.
idinfo.datacred: Data collected and compiled by Analytical Surveys, Inc. of Colorado Springs, Colorado and maintained as needed by the City of Norfolk.
